        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your cilia are sensitive to detecting electric signatures of nearby creatures. You gain electromagnetic sense as an imprecise sense with a range of 15 feet. Electromagnetic sense allows you to detect nearby creatures and technological objects, but you might have to use the [[/act seek]] action to find an undetected creature in an environment with too much electromagnetic radiation, such as inside the engine room of a starship or near a powerful source of radio waves.</p>"
